<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Event Showcase</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"
        integrity="sha512-DTOQO9RWCH3ppGqcWaEA1BIZOC6xxalwEsw9c2QQeAIftl+Vegovlnee1c9QX4TctnWMn13TZye+giMm8e2LwA=="
        crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Marhey:wght@300..700&family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap');
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Caveat:wght@500&display=swap');
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat&display=swap');
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bad+Script&family=Charm&family=Leckerli+One&family=Open+Sans:wght@300&family=Satisfy&display=swap');
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Ephesis&display=swap');
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap');
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Marhey:wght@300..700&family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
            font-optical-sizing: auto;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-image: url(../res/bg.jpg);
            color: #fff;
            position: relative;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-position: center;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #0000006c;
            font-family: "Marhey", sans-serif;
        }

        .logoDiv {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 150px;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 200px;
        }

        header li {
            list-style: none;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-family: var(--main-font);
        }

        header a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-family: var(--main-font);
            font-weight: var(--main-weight-a);
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: orange;
        }

        header {
            position: relative;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        .navbar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 75px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .navbar .links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .navbar .toggle_btn {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: none;
        }

        .action_btn {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.273);
            font-family: var(--main-font);
            color: rgb(255, 248, 125);
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .action_btn:hover {
            scale: 1.05;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .action_btn:active {
            scale: 0.95;
        }

        .dropdown_menu {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            right: 2rem;
            top: 60px;
            height: 0;
            width: 300px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.021);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: height 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            z-index: 3;
        }

        .dropdown_menu.open {
            height: 240px;
        }

        .dropdown_menu li {
            padding: 5px 0.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .dropdown_menu .action_btn {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.536);
            color: rgb(255, 248, 125);
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .dropdown_menu .dd_btn {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #ffffff00;
        }


        @media(max-width: 992px) {

            .navbar .links,
            .navbar .action_btn {
                display: none;
            }

            .navbar .toggle_btn {
                display: block;
            }

            .dropdown_menu {
                display: block;

            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .dropdown_menu {
                left: 2rem;
                width: unset;
            }
        }

        .container {
            margin: 5vmin;
            padding: 6vmin;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.580);
            border-radius: 17px;
        }

        .enroll {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: left;
            align-items: last baseline;
            height: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .regButton {
            padding: 5px 20px;
            text-decoration:none;
            font-family: "Marhey", sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
            border: 0px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.603);
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.603);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="navbar">
            <div class="logoDiv"><img src="../res/logo.png" alt="logo" class="logo"></div>
            <ul class="links">
                <li><a href="/events">Events</a></li>
                <li><a href="/caportal">CA Portal</a></li>
                <li><a href="/sponsor">Sponsors</a></li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/profile" class="action_btn">profile</a>
            <div class="toggle_btn">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="dropdown_menu">
            <li><a href="/events" class="dd_btn">Events</a></li>
            <li><a href="/caportal" class="dd_btn">CA Portal</a></li>
            <li><a href="/sponsor" class="dd_btn">Sponsors</a></li>
            <li><a href="/profile" class="action_btn">profile</a></li>
        </div>
    </header>


    <div class="container">
        <div class="heading">
            <h1>Safarnama</h1>
            <h2>(Short Film)</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            “Relating a person to the whole world; that is the meaning of film.”
            It's true, isn't it? For once in our day-to-day thought processing, we all have wondered what
            would happen if this were not our life or the story that we are processing, and we could actually
            direct our own chronicle here… So, Encore'24 is giving all of you an opportunity to create your
            own visual style of cinematics and let it be unique for yourself yet identifiable to the audience.
            Just wear your director's hat, plot your script well with the perfect tone of dialogues, and then
            maybe, who knows, you become the director who was not inspired but the one who actually
            inspired others.
        </div>
        <div class="heading">
            <h2>Rulebook</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            1. Theme: Open <br>
            2. Duration: The short film should be up to 10 minutes, including titles and production everything. <br>
            3. It should be suitable for everyone (No nudity, no obscenity, no excessive violence, less use of
            cuss words as much as possible). <br>
            4. Maximum 5 people can make a team to take part in the competition. <br>
            5. It's necessary that during screening, the director and the spokesperson be present. <br>
            6. Only one entry of each short film maker will be entertained. <br>
            7. The plot should be original, Plagiarism is a big no-no here. <br>
            8. Submitted short films with Full HD 1080p or 720p and 16:9 aspect ratios would be better. <br>
            9. Decisions taken by our respected jury will be final. <br>
            10. Any camera may be used (Digital SLRs, Mobile Camera, etc.) to shoot the film. <br>
            11. Participants have to submit their short film online at email id of encore 3 days within
            the commencement of the event. <br>
            12. Communication: Mention your email ids and WhatsApp number for contact purposes. <br>
            13. Abide by all the rules or you will be disqualified. <br>
            <br>
            Bonus credits if you try on these themes: <br>
            1. Animation on any famous film. <br>
            2. Same-gender marriage. <br>
            3. Advertisement or commercial on any famous brand. <br>
            … … Many more topics like such if we include this bonus credits part. <br>
        </div>
        <div class="enroll">
            <a href="/enrolling/short_film" class="regButton"><%=BtnName%></a>
        </div>
    </div>


    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/536b7f8348.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script>
        const toggleBtn = document.querySelector('.toggle_btn')
        const toggleBtnTcon = document.querySelector('.toggle_btn i')
        const dropDownMenu = document.querySelector('.dropdown_menu')

        toggleBtn.onclick = function () {
            dropDownMenu.classList.toggle('open')
        }
    </script>
</body>

</html>